Treasury balances at the FederalReserve rose on March 12 to 3.038 billion dlrs on March 12 from2.715 billion dlrs the previous business day, the Treasury saidin its latest budget statement.    Balances in tax and loan note accounts fell to 7.623billion dlrs from 8.870 billion dlrs on the same respectivedays.    The Treasury's operating cash balance totaled 10.661billion dlrs on March 12 compared with 11.586 billion dlrs onMarch 11. Reuter&#3;